task.summary: Default task
Fix more build errors (only 98 left outside tests!); implement SoftCache and font-related methods of GraphicsEnvironment; eliminate more dead code in sun.*
Remove dependencies of sun.awt.im.CompositionArea on Swing
Delete demos for now. (Some can be added back later, once we figure out which ones can use an Android app as an entry point.)
Fix all remaining compiler errors in src/share. Eliminate more dead code.
SkinJobGraphics now extends Graphics2D, giving it a more powerful interface.
Delete sun.java2d; migrate classes to use Shape instead of Region; finish SkinJobMenuPeer.
Delete sun.java2d; migrate classes to use Shape instead of Region; finish SkinJobMenuPeer.
Minor fixes
Add output folder to .hgignore
Delete make folder, since it's almost all specific to non-Android OSs. Delete upstream TODOs, since they're out of scope for SkinJob.
Remove dependency of DropTarget on Swing Timer. Extract timing magic numbers from DropTarget.

Fix SkinJobCanvasPeer to use a View, since a java.awt.Canvas is defined as being on a screen. Rewrite getAppropriateGraphicsConfiguration to ensure that it returns a SkinJobGraphicsConfiguration for the corresponding screen. Pull out Shape boolean-operation stubs into a SkinJobGeometry class.
Remove more dead code.
Remove more dead code; implement some font-related methods.
Implement TextLineComponent.subset; perform various refactorings.
Implement methods of GraphicComponent.
equals and hashCode for GraphicComponent and TextLineComponent
Attempt to display the file picker for FileDialog. Implement dashes and XOR mode in SkinJobGraphics.
Implement SkinJobTextFieldPeer.setEchoChar.
More details on design goals.
More details on design goals.
Organize SkinJob into packages, and document the package structure.
Eliminate SunToolkit, except for some static methods.
Implement SkinJobSystemTrayPeer (a "system-tray icon" is a Notification).
Fix initialization of sjAndroidWidget and sjAndroidContext on deserialization.
Implement readObjectNoData, and document the serialization-compatibility question.
Fix build errors
Merge Sun code into sun.* to complete some TODOs
Merge Sun code into sun.* to complete some TODOs
Eliminate a walled-garden group of classes from sun.awt.image.
Eliminate 2 unused classes from sun.awt.image.
Merge in javax.print.attribute.standard.MediaPrintableArea, completing a TODO and fixing a bug where the native unit was previously 1 mm rather than 0.001 mm.
Add SkinJobAndroidBitmapWrapper interface, implemented by SkinJobBufferedImage and SkinJobVolatileImage. Consolidate some TODOs.
Remove more dead code from sun.awt.*.
Fix build errors.
Consolidate implementations of ContainerPeer. Implement some bounds-related methods in SkinJobWindowPeer.
Add TODO to apply transform in more methods of SkinJobGraphics
Implement toAndroidBitmap(RenderedImage) in terms of toAndroidBitmap(Image) and SkinJobBufferedImage.setData(Raster)
Handle ImageObserver parameter properly in SkinJobGraphics. Implement asAndroidBitmap(Image) for param that is a RenderedImage, even if it's not a SkinJobAndroidBitmapWrapper.
setFont in peer classes now works properly.
Implement SkinJobWindowPeer.paint(Graphics)
setFont is now a no-op on elements without a stylable label.
Tentatively fix a label alignment bug.
Partly implement createStrokedShape using MarlinRenderingEngine code.
Implement SkinJobGraphics.draw(Shape) and fill(Shape) by translating the PathIterator to an android.graphics.Path.
Eliminate more dead code. Implement TODO methods in AttributeValues.
Attempt to migrate to Gradle. Committing despite broken status so that I can ask for help with debugging,
WrappedAndroidObjectsSupplier doesn't need to implement Serializable and isn't well-suited to doing so.
